data.eml:eml: Occurrence of Millotellina (Myriapoda, Symphyla) in China with the description of two new species

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Jin, Ya-Li, Bu, Yun (2019): Occurrence of Millotellina (Myriapoda, Symphyla) in China with the description of two new species. Zootaxa 4691 (3): 215-224, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4691.3.2
